# eADV

## Example

```html
<amp-ad
  width="300"
  height="250"
  type="eadv"
  data-x="7f-11322-ce-2-a3-0-d4-23-d6-300x250-db-0-da"
  data-u="etaid.v"
>
</amp-ad>
```

## Configuration

For details on the configuration semantics, please contact the ad network or refer to their documentation.

Supported parameters:

-   `data-x`
-   `data-u`
